n.com/thumbor/ItHPC_rALXdOcdWytBMHEFZoqcQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73159360/acastro_STK083_01.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;xDiqqn&quot;>;Nvidia 市值已正式突破 2 万亿美元，成为第一家跨过这一门槛的芯片制造商。它也是第三家估值超过 2 万亿美元的美国公司，仅次于苹果（&lt;a href=&quot;https://ycharts.com/companies/AAPL/market_cap&quot;>;2.83 万亿美元&lt;/a>;）和微软（&lt;a href=&quot;https://ycharts.com/companies/MSFT/market_cap&quot;>;3.06 万亿美元&lt;/a>;)。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NQQnWq&quot;>;这家总部位于加州的公司在过去经历了快速增长凭借其在人工智能芯片市场的领先地位。 Nvidia 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/30/23742123/nvidia-stock-ai-gpu-1-trillion-market-cap-price-value&quot;>;市值达到 1 万亿美元&lt;/a>; 仅仅不到一年前，它就离开了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/14/24073384/nvidia-market-cap-passes-amazon-alphabet&quot;>;亚马逊和 Alphabet 都在后视镜中，因为本月早些时候它成为一家价值 1.83 万亿美元的公司。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;SBACLf &quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&quot;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;人工智能的狂热让投资者的期望很高。财报电话会议令人失望.&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24075086/ai-investment-hype-earnings&quot;}]}&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;8wyD5k&quot;>;作为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/21/24079546/generative-ai-has-hit-the-tipping-point&quot;>;其收益报告的一部分上周&lt;/a>;，Nvidia 公布 2023 年收入创纪录的 609 亿美元，较 2022 年增长 126%。其他公司，如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/19 /24044319/openai-chip-manufacturing-fundraise&quot;>;OpenAI&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/21/24079336/microsoft-intel-chip-partnership-foundry -tsmc&quot;>;微软和...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/23/24080975/nvidia-ai-chips- h100-h200-市值&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/23/24080975/nvidia-ai-chips-h100-h200-market-capitalization" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/23/24080975/nvidia-ai-chips-h100-h200-market-capitalization</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>